sub_title: MSc Biomedical Science (Drug Safety and Toxicology) at the Radboud University
summary: I am currently doing my Master's program in Biomedical Sciences at the Radboud University, Nijmegen (Netherlands), with a specialization in Drug Safety and Toxicology and a Research profile. As part of this masters I am performing an internship at the Max-Planck Research Unit for Neurogenetics in Frankfurt (Main).
